name: PHASE01_EGG: “The Nechrysalis”
description: GUIDE TO THE COMPLETE METAMORPHOSIS OF THE MODERN WORLD ENDER. The Nechrysalis’ is a play on the Greek root ‘nec’ , referring to death and the ‘chrysalis’ which is a quiescent insect development state. This is the first stage of the modern World Ender’s metamorphosis. The Nechrysalis presents the life of the emerging beast from the egg and the inevitable destruction it will bring upon the world.
